<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.4.1">
<l>pukaḻunal loruva ṉeṉkō poruvilcīrp pūmi yeṉkō</l>
<l>tikaḻuntaṇ paravai yeṉkō tīyeṉkō vāyu veṉkō</l>
<l>nikaḻumā kāca meṉkō nīḷcuṭa riraṇṭu meṉkō</l>
<l>vikaḻviliv vaṉaittu meṉkō kaṇṇaṉaik kūvu māṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will I say “the one good one who is praised“? Will I say “earth of incomparable excellence”?</l>
<l>Will I say “glittering cool expanse“ ? Will I say “fire”? Will I say “wind”?</l>
<l>Will I say “floating room”? Will I say “two long lights”?</l>  
<l>Will I say all these things without negligence, the way I call Kṛṣṇa?</l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
